lyrics:
[Verse]
Lucas hates the banjo, it's a mystery why
He never felt its magic, never gave it a try
Its twang and its rhythm, he just can't embrace
But the banjo keeps playing, with a smile on its face

[Chorus]
Lucas hates the banjo, but it keeps on strummin
Its joyful melodies, to his ears it's hummin
The banjo's gonna sing, with or without him
Oh Lucas hates the banjo, but its spirit won't dim
